simulations.title: bonn3600ket
simulations.omnetppini:
[General]
network = OPSNetwork



#simulation control parameters
sim-time-limit = 604800s # 7 days
repeat = 1



# RNG initialization
num-rngs = 6
seed-0-mt = 1000   # left specifically unused for "unknown" RNG uses
seed-1-mt = 2000   # application
seed-2-mt = 3000   # user behaviour model RNG
seed-3-mt = 4000   # forwarding RNG
seed-4-mt = 5000   # link layer RNG
seed-5-mt = 6000   # mobility RNG



# results location
result-dir = results/
output-vector-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.vec"
output-scalar-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.sca"



# statistic collection
**.vector-recording = true
**.scalar-recording = true
**.statistic-recording = true


[Config Herald-Keetchi-BONN]

# network parameters
**.numNodes = 3600

# application layer (herald)
**.applicationLayer = "KHeraldApp"
**.app.ttl = 259200 # 3 days
**.app.popularityAssignmentPercentage = 25
**.app.dataGenerationInterval = 90s
**.app.dataSizeInBytes = 100000
**.app.usedRNG = 1
**.app.dataGenerationIntervalMode = "trace"
**.app.trafficInfoPath = "/opt/traces/benchmarks/scenario-02-typhoon/Scenario"


# Keetchi forwarding
**.forwardingLayer = "KKeetchiLayer"
**.forwarding.agingInterval = 600s
**.forwarding.maximumCacheSize = 10000000byte
**.forwarding.neighbourhoodChangeSignificanceThreshold = 0.25
**.forwarding.coolOffDuration = 300s
**.forwarding.learningConst = 0.5
**.forwarding.backoffTimerIncrementFactor = 1.5
**.forwarding.usedRNG = 3

# wireless interface parameters
**.linkLayer = "KWirelessInterface"
**.link.wirelessRange = 30m
**.link.neighbourScanInterval = 1s
**.link.bandwidthBitRate = 100000bps
**.link.wirelessHeaderSize = 16byte
**.link.usedRNG = 4

## mobility parameters for BonnMotion
**.mobilityType = "BonnMotionMobility"
**.mobility.traceFile = "/opt/traces/benchmarks/scenario-02-typhoon/Trace/halong.movements"
**.mobility.nodeId = -1 #means "host module's index"

simulations.title: TraceRollerPro62
simulations.omnetppini:
[General]
network = OPSNetwork



#simulation control parameters
sim-time-limit = 10800s # 3 hrs
repeat = 1



# RNG initialization
num-rngs = 6
seed-0-mt = 1000   # left specifically unused for "unknown" RNG uses
seed-1-mt = 2000   # application
seed-2-mt = 3000   # user behaviour model RNG
seed-3-mt = 4000   # forwarding RNG
seed-4-mt = 5000   # link layer RNG
seed-5-mt = 6000   # mobility RNG



# results location
result-dir = results/
output-vector-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.vec"
output-scalar-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.sca"



# statistic collection
**.vector-recording = true
**.scalar-recording = true
**.statistic-recording = true


[Config messenger-1s-Prophet-62-nodes]

# network parameters
**.numNodes = 62

# application layer (messenger)
**.applicationLayer = "KMessengerApp"
**.app.dataGenerationInterval = 1s
**.app.dataSizeInBytes = 1000000
**.app.usedRNG = 1
**.app.dataGenerationIntervalMode = "trace"
**.app.trafficInfoPath = "/opt/traces/benchmarks/scenario-06-roller-skate/Scenario"

# forwarding layer parameters
**.forwardingLayer = "KProphetRoutingLayer"
**.forwarding.maximumCacheSize = 5000000byte
**.forwarding.antiEntropyInterval = 300s
**.forwarding.maximumHopCount = 25
**.forwarding.usedRNG = 3
**.forwarding.pEncounterMax = 0.7
**.forwarding.pEncounterFirst = 0.5
**.forwarding.pFirstThreshold = 0.1
**.forwarding.alpha = 0.5
**.forwarding.beta = 0.9
**.forwarding.gamma = 0.998
**.forwarding.delta = 0.1
**.forwarding.standardTimeInterval = 3600s

# wireless interface parameters
**.linkLayer = "KWirelessInterfaceWithContactTraces"
**.link.wirelessRange = 30m
**.link.neighbourScanInterval = 1s
**.link.bandwidthBitRate = 100000bps
**.link.wirelessHeaderSize = 16byte
**.link.usedRNG = 4
**.link.contactTracesPath = "/opt/traces/benchmarks/scenario-06-roller-skate/Trace"

**.constraintAreaMinX = 0m
**.constraintAreaMinY = 0m
**.constraintAreaMinZ = 0m
**.constraintAreaMaxX = 1500m
**.constraintAreaMaxY = 1500m
**.constraintAreaMaxZ = 0m

**.mobilityType = "SWIMMobility"
**.mobility.noOfLocations = 150
**.mobility.Hosts = 600
**.mobility.popularityDecisionThreshold = 7
**.mobility.returnHomePercentage = 15
**.mobility.neighbourLocationLimit = 200m
**.mobility.speed = 15mps
**.mobility.radius = 2m
**.mobility.alpha = 0.5
**.mobility.waitTime = uniform(1200s, 28800s, 5) # 20 mins - 8 hrs
**.mobility.usedRNG = 5

[General]
network = OPSNetwork

#simulation control parameters
sim-time-limit = 604800s # 7 days
repeat = 1

# RNG initialization
num-rngs = 6
seed-0-mt = 1000 # left specifically unused for "unknown" RNG uses
seed-1-mt = 2000 # application
seed-2-mt = 3000 # user behaviour model RNG
seed-3-mt = 4000 # forwarding RNG
seed-4-mt = 5000 # link layer RNG
seed-5-mt = 6000 # mobility RNG

# results location
result-dir = results/
output-vector-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.vec"
output-scalar-file = "${resultdir}/${inifile}-${configname}-${runnumber}.sca"

# statistic collection
**.vector-recording = true
**.scalar-recording = true
**.statistic-recording = true

[Config Herald-Prophet-SWIM]

# network parameters
**.numNodes = 25

# application layer (herald)
**.applicationLayer = "KHeraldApp"
**.app.ttl = 259200
**.app.popularityAssignmentPercentage = 25
**.app.dataGenerationInterval = 90s
**.app.dataSizeInBytes = 10000
**.app.usedRNG = 1

# forwarding layer parameters
**.forwardingLayer = "KProphetRoutingLayer"
**.forwarding.maximumCacheSize = 500000byte
**.forwarding.antiEntropyInterval = 300s
**.forwarding.maximumHopCount = 25
**.forwarding.usedRNG = 3
**.forwarding.pEncounterMax = 0.7
**.forwarding.pEncounterFirst = 0.5
**.forwarding.pFirstThreshold = 0.1
**.forwarding.alpha = 0.5
**.forwarding.beta = 0.9
**.forwarding.gamma = 0.998
**.forwarding.delta = 0.1
**.forwarding.standardTimeInterval = 3600s

# wireless interface parameters

**.link.wirelessRange = 30m
**.link.neighbourScanInterval = 1s
**.link.bandwidthBitRate = 100000bps
**.link.wirelessHeaderSize = 16byte

**.constraintAreaMinX = 0m
**.constraintAreaMinY = 0m
**.constraintAreaMinZ = 0m
**.constraintAreaMaxX = 500m
**.constraintAreaMaxY = 500m
**.constraintAreaMaxZ = 0m

**.mobility.alpha = 0.5
**.mobility.waitTime = uniform(1200s, 28800s, 5)
**.mobility.usedRNG = 5
